<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!--
File Name: FemurFracturePlanner.ui
Version: v0.300
Date: 2026-06-23
Description: Femur Fracture Planner 모듈의 Qt UI 레이아웃 파일

Version History:

- v0.300 (2026-06-23)
  - 6. Virtual Bone Reduction 내에 파편 조각 간 절단면을 직접 맞물려 밀착 정합시키는 Run Fracture Surface Snap 버튼(runSurfaceSnapButton) 추가 (X 증가, Y/Z 초기화)
- v0.200 (2026-06-23)
  - 7. Fragment Manager 내부에 각 프래그먼트의 실시간 3D 위치 및 회전을 표시해 주는 transformDisplayGroupBox UI 신설 (X 증가, Y/Z 초기화)
- v0.180 (2026-06-23)
  - 좌측 QScrollArea 스크롤바를 완전히 제거(롤백)하고 세로 창 크기 직접 확장 방식으로 회귀 (Y 증가, Z 초기화)
- v0.170 (2026-06-23)
  - 7. Fragment Manager 테이블 컬럼 개수 확장(5개) 및 수동 정렬 기즈모 컬럼을 위해 columnCount를 5로 변경 (Y 증가, Z 초기화)
- v0.120 (2026-06-23)
  - 6번 가이드 모델 선택기 옆에 가시성 제어 버튼(guideVisibilityButton) 추가 (Y 증가, Z 초기화)
- v0.101 (2026-06-23)
  - 팝업 다이얼로그 기본 세로 높이를 700에서 830으로 확장 (Z 증가)
- v0.091 (2026-06-23)
  - 7. Fragment Manager 섹션 하단에 일괄 초기화 버튼(clearModelsButton) 추가 (Y 증가 후 Z 증가이지만 Y 증가로 처리)
- v0.090 (2026-06-23)
  - 5~7번 단계를 오른쪽 컬럼으로 배치하는 2컬럼 레이아웃 적용 및 가이드 모델 로더 버튼(loadGuideButton) 추가 (Y 증가, Z 초기화)
- v0.080 (2026-06-23)
  - 7. Fragment Manager 섹션 및 QTableWidget 추가, 팝업 기본 크기 확장(420x850) (Y 증가, Z 초기화)
- v0.031 (2026-06-23)
  - UI XML 문법 오류 수정 (Z 증가)
- v0.030 (2026-06-23)
  - 6. Virtual Bone Reduction UI 섹션 및 위젯 추가 배치 (Y 증가, Z 초기화)
- v0.020 (2026-06-23)
  - DICOM 데이터베이스 로더 버튼(loadDicomButton) 추가 배치 (Y 증가, Z 초기화)
- v0.010 (2026-06-23)
  - 다이렉트 파일 로더 버튼(loadVolumeButton) 배치 및 3D 뷰 회전/세그먼트 에디터 레이아웃 구성 (Y 증가, Z 초기화)
- v0.000 (2026-06-23)
  - 최초 작성
-->
<ui version="4.0">
 <class>FemurFracturePlanner</class>
 <widget class="qMRMLWidget" name="FemurFracturePlanner">
  <property name="geometry">
   <rect>
    <x>0</x>
    <y>0</y>
    <width>850</width>
    <height>830</height>
   </rect>
  </property>
  <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="mainHLayout">
   
   <!-- Left Column (Steps 1 to 4) -->
   <item>
    <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="leftVLayout">
     
     <!-- 1. Input CT Volume Selection with Eye Toggle & File Loader -->
     <item>
      <widget class="ctkCollapsibleButton" name="inputCollapsibleButton">
       <property name="text">
        <string>1. Input CT Volume</string>
       </property>
       <layout class="QFormLayout" name="inputFormLayout">
        <item row="0" column="0">
         <widget class="QLabel" name="inputVolumeLabel">
          <property name="text">
           <string>Input Volume:</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
        <item row="0" column="1">
         <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="volumeSelectHLayout">
          <item>
           <widget class="qMRMLNodeComboBox" name="inputVolumeSelector">
            <property name="toolTip">
             <string>Select the input CT volume node.</string>
            </property>
            <property name="nodeTypes">
             <stringlist notr="true">
              <string>vtkMRMLScalarVolumeNode</string>
             </stringlist>
            </property>
            <property name="showChildNodeTypes">
             <bool>false</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="addEnabled">
             <bool>false</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="removeEnabled">
             <bool>false</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="SlicerParameterName" stdset="0">
             <string>inputVolume</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item>
           <widget class="QPushButton" name="volumeVisibilityButton">
            <property name="text">
             <string>Show</string>
            </property>
            <property name="checkable">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="toolTip">
             <string>Toggle volume visibility in slice viewers.</string>
            </property>
            <property name="maximumSize">
             <size>
              <width>60</width>
              <height>16777215</height>
             </size>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </item>
        <item row="1" column="0" colspan="2">
         <widget class="QPushButton" name="loadVolumeButton">
          <property name="text">
           <string>📁 Load CT Volume (File)</string>
          </property>
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>Load a CT volume file (.nrrd, .nii, .nii.gz, etc.) from local storage.</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
        <item row="2" column="0" colspan="2">
         <widget class="QPushButton" name="loadDicomButton">
          <property name="text">
           <string>📁 Load CT Volume (DICOM DB)</string>
          </property>
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>Open Slicer's DICOM database browser in a popup dialog to load volumes.</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
       </layout>
      </widget>
     </item>

     <!-- 2. Real-time 3D Volume Rendering -->
     <item>
      <widget class="ctkCollapsibleButton" name="renderingCollapsibleButton">
       <property name="text">
        <string>2. 3D Volume Rendering (CT-Bone)</string>
       </property>
       <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="renderingVLayout">
        <item>
         <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="switchHLayout">
          <item>
           <widget class="QLabel" name="enableRenderingLabel">
            <property name="text">
             <string>Volume Rendering Visibility:</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item>
           <widget class="QPushButton" name="volumeRenderingVisibilityButton">
            <property name="text">
             <string>👁️ Show</string>
            </property>
            <property name="checkable">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="toolTip">
             <string>Toggle 3D volume rendering visibility.</string>
            </property>
            <property name="maximumSize">
             <size>
              <width>80</width>
              <height>16777215</height>
             </size>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </item>
        <item>
         <layout class="QFormLayout" name="thresholdFormLayout">
          <item row="0" column="0">
           <widget class="QLabel" name="thresholdLabel">
            <property name="text">
             <string>Threshold (HU):</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item row="0" column="1">
           <widget class="ctkSliderWidget" name="thresholdSlider">
            <property name="toolTip">
             <string>Adjust bone visibility threshold in real-time.</string>
            </property>
            <property name="minimum">
             <double>100</double>
            </property>
            <property name="maximum">
             <double>1500</double>
            </property>
            <property name="value">
             <double>200</double>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </item>
       </layout>
      </widget>
     </item>

     <!-- 3. Image Rotation Control -->
     <item>
      <widget class="ctkCollapsibleButton" name="rotationCollapsibleButton">
       <property name="text">
        <string>3. Live 3D Rotation Control</string>
       </property>
       <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="rotationVLayout">
        <item>
         <widget class="QGroupBox" name="axisGroupBox">
          <property name="title">
           <string>Rotation Axis</string>
          </property>
          <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="axisHLayout">
           <item>
            <widget class="QRadioButton" name="rotationXRadio">
             <property name="text">
              <string>X-Axis</string>
             </property>
             <property name="checked">
              <bool>true</bool>
             </property>
            </widget>
           </item>
           <item>
            <widget class="QRadioButton" name="rotationYRadio">
             <property name="text">
              <string>Y-Axis</string>
             </property>
            </widget>
           </item>
           <item>
            <widget class="QRadioButton" name="rotationZRadio">
             <property name="text">
              <string>Z-Axis</string>
             </property>
            </widget>
           </item>
          </layout>
         </widget>
        </item>
        <item>
         <layout class="QFormLayout" name="fineRotationLayout">
          <item row="0" column="0">
           <widget class="QLabel" name="angleLabel">
            <property name="text">
             <string>Angle (°):</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item row="0" column="1">
           <widget class="ctkSliderWidget" name="rotationAngleSlider">
            <property name="toolTip">
             <string>Rotate the volume interactively.</string>
            </property>
            <property name="minimum">
             <double>-180</double>
            </property>
            <property name="maximum">
             <double>180</double>
            </property>
            <property name="value">
             <double>0</double>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </item>
        <item>
         <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="rotationButtonsLayout">
          <item>
           <widget class="QPushButton" name="resetRotationButton">
            <property name="text">
             <string>Reset (0°)</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item>
           <widget class="QPushButton" name="rotate90Button">
            <property name="text">
             <string>Rotate +90°</string>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </item>
       </layout>
      </widget>
     </item>

     <!-- 4. Embedded Segment Editor -->
     <item>
      <widget class="ctkCollapsibleButton" name="segmentEditorCollapsibleButton">
       <property name="text">
        <string>4. Embedded Segment Editor</string>
       </property>
       <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="editorVLayout">
        <item>
         <widget class="QWidget" name="segmentEditorAnchorWidget" native="true">
          <property name="minimumSize">
           <size>
            <width>0</width>
            <height>350</height>
           </size>
          </property>
          <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="anchorVLayout">
           <property name="spacing">
            <number>0</number>
           </property>
           <property name="leftMargin">
            <number>0</number>
           </property>
           <property name="topMargin">
            <number>0</number>
           </property>
           <property name="rightMargin">
            <number>0</number>
           </property>
           <property name="bottomMargin">
            <number>0</number>
           </property>
          </layout>
         </widget>
        </item>
       </layout>
       </widget>
      </item>
     </layout>
    </item>

   <!-- Right Column (Steps 5 to 7) -->
   <item>
    <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="rightVLayout">
     
     <!-- 5. Fracture Fragment Separation -->
     <item>
      <widget class="ctkCollapsibleButton" name="fragmentSeparationCollapsibleButton">
       <property name="text">
        <string>5. Fracture Fragment Separation</string>
       </property>
       <layout class="QFormLayout" name="separationFormLayout">
        <item row="0" column="0">
         <widget class="QLabel" name="targetSegmentationLabel">
          <property name="text">
           <string>Input Segmentation:</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
        <item row="0" column="1">
         <widget class="qMRMLNodeComboBox" name="activeSegmentationSelector">
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>Select the segmentation node to separate disjoint components.</string>
          </property>
          <property name="nodeTypes">
           <stringlist notr="true">
            <string>vtkMRMLSegmentationNode</string>
           </stringlist>
          </property>
          <property name="showChildNodeTypes">
           <bool>false</bool>
          </property>
          <property name="addEnabled">
           <bool>false</bool>
          </property>
          <property name="removeEnabled">
           <bool>false</bool>
          </property>
          <property name="noneEnabled">
           <bool>true</bool>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
        <item row="1" column="0" colspan="2">
         <widget class="QPushButton" name="separateFragmentsButton">
          <property name="text">
           <string>Separate Bone Fragments</string>
          </property>
          <property name="styleSheet">
           <string>font-weight: bold; background-color: #fff3e0;</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
       </layout>
      </widget>
     </item>

     <!-- 6. Virtual Bone Reduction -->
     <item>
      <widget class="ctkCollapsibleButton" name="virtualReductionCollapsibleButton">
       <property name="text">
        <string>6. Virtual Bone Reduction</string>
       </property>
       <layout class="QFormLayout" name="reductionFormLayout">
        <item row="0" column="0">
         <widget class="QLabel" name="guideModelLabel">
          <property name="text">
           <string>Guide Model:</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
        <item row="0" column="1">
         <layout class="QHBoxLayout" name="guideSelectHLayout">
          <item>
           <widget class="qMRMLNodeComboBox" name="guideModelSelector">
            <property name="toolTip">
             <string>Select the template guide bone model (e.g. contralateral normal bone).</string>
            </property>
            <property name="nodeTypes">
             <stringlist notr="true">
              <string>vtkMRMLModelNode</string>
             </stringlist>
            </property>
            <property name="showChildNodeTypes">
             <bool>false</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="addEnabled">
             <bool>false</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="removeEnabled">
             <bool>false</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="noneEnabled">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item>
           <widget class="QPushButton" name="guideVisibilityButton">
            <property name="text">
             <string>Show</string>
            </property>
            <property name="checkable">
             <bool>true</bool>
            </property>
            <property name="toolTip">
             <string>Toggle guide model visibility in 3D and 2D viewers.</string>
            </property>
            <property name="maximumSize">
             <size>
              <width>60</width>
              <height>16777215</height>
             </size>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
          <item>
           <widget class="QPushButton" name="loadGuideButton">
            <property name="text">
             <string>📁 Add Data</string>
            </property>
            <property name="toolTip">
             <string>Load a guide bone model file (.stl, .obj, .ply) from local storage.</string>
            </property>
            <property name="maximumSize">
             <size>
              <width>85</width>
              <height>16777215</height>
             </size>
            </property>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </item>
        <item row="1" column="0" colspan="2">
         <widget class="QPushButton" name="mirrorGuideButton">
          <property name="text">
           <string>Mirror Guide (Flip X)</string>
          </property>
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>Mirror the selected guide model along the X axis.</string>
          </property>
          <property name="styleSheet">
           <string>font-weight: bold; background-color: #e3f2fd;</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
        <item row="2" column="0" colspan="2">
         <widget class="QPushButton" name="runSurfaceSnapButton">
          <property name="text">
           <string>Run Fracture Surface Snap</string>
          </property>
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>Align the fracture surfaces of the fragments directly before guide reduction.</string>
          </property>
          <property name="styleSheet">
           <string>font-weight: bold; background-color: #fff8e1; border: 1px solid #ffe082; padding: 3px;</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
        <item row="3" column="0" colspan="2">
         <widget class="QPushButton" name="runIcpReductionButton">
          <property name="text">
           <string>Run ICP Auto-Reduction</string>
          </property>
          <property name="toolTip">
           <string>Automatically align separated fragment models to the guide model using ICP.</string>
          </property>
          <property name="styleSheet">
           <string>font-weight: bold; background-color: #e8f5e9;</string>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
       </layout>
      </widget>
     </item>

     <!-- 7. Fragment Manager -->
     <item>
      <widget class="ctkCollapsibleButton" name="fragmentManagerCollapsibleButton">
       <property name="text">
        <string>7. Fragment Manager</string>
       </property>
       <layout class="QVBoxLayout" name="managerVLayout">
        <item>
         <widget class="QTableWidget" name="fragmentTableWidget">
          <property name="minimumSize">
           <size>
            <width>0</width>
            <height>180</height>
           </size>
          </property>
          <property name="columnCount">
           <number>5</number>
          </property>
         </widget>
        </item>
        <item>
         <widget class="QGroupBox" name="transformDisplayGroupBox">
          <property name="title">
           <string>Selected Fragment Position &amp; Rotation (Real-time)</string>
          </property>
          <property name="styleSheet">
           <string>QGroupBox { font-weight: bold; color: #1565c0; border: 1px solid #bbdefb; border-radius: 5px; margin-top: 10px; padding-top: 10px; } QGroupBox::title { subcontrol-origin: margin; left: 10px; padding: 0 3px; }</string>
